gobblin.runtime.api

Class FlowSpec.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.runtime.api.FlowSpec.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    FlowSpec

    public static class FlowSpec.Builder
extends Object
    Builder for FlowSpecs.

    Defaults/conventions:

    • Default flowCatalogURI is DEFAULT_FLOW_CATALOG_SCHEME:
    • Convention for FlowSpec URI: /config.get(ConfigurationKeys.FLOW_GROUP_KEY)/config.get(ConfigurationKeys.FLOW_NAME_KEY)
    • Convention for Description: config.get(ConfigurationKeys.FLOW_DESCRIPTION_KEY)
    • Default version: 1
